divs: Sighting DetailsSo I'm walking to the pet store, looking directly west. I noticed they were going crazy trying to cover the sky with chemtrails. I was wondering why when all the sudden I look up and what do I see. A very fast moving white UFO like the ones in Britain moving away from a helicopter. It was traveling South West until it went into the clouds. The jet was right behind it trying to spray and catch up I guess. It was pretty amazing. I live in Timmins, Ontario. Let me know if anyone messages you with a sighting today! This was at approx. 12:30 to 1 pm today (july 9 2011) Dave
